Create ANNEM Summary Report

Source: R/annem_analysis.R
create_annem_summary_report.Rd

Generate a comprehensive text summary report of ANNEM analysis results.

create_annem_summary_report(
  market,
  agent_performance,
  network_metrics,
  benchmark_comparison,
  validation_results,
  output_dir
)

Arguments

market

ANNEMMarket object

agent_performance

Agent performance data frame

network_metrics

Network evolution metrics

benchmark_comparison

Model comparison results

validation_results

Framework validation results

output_dir

Directory to save the report
